I am not submitting this map, it is just a little walls map me and my friend made and it completely operates on redstone.
I didn't bother showing the redstone because most people will most likely not get it or understand how it works.


Tell me what you think? also the center area is being made a walls template and can be expanded if your interested I can make a download link.
